graph LR
    Notebooks[Workbench Images<br/>Notebooks]

    %% External Dependencies (Required at Build/Runtime)
    Notebooks -->|base OS| UBI9[UBI9 Python Image<br/>registry.access.redhat.com<br/>Python 3.9/3.11]
    Notebooks -->|IDE| JupyterLab[JupyterLab 3.6.7<br/>Jupyter Server 2.13.0]
    Notebooks -->|IDE| CodeServer[code-server v4.22.0<br/>VS Code in Browser]
    Notebooks -->|IDE| RStudioServer[RStudio Server<br/>2023.12.1-402]
    Notebooks -->|reverse proxy| NGINX[NGINX 1.24<br/>CodeServer/RStudio]
    Notebooks -->|process mgmt| supervisord[supervisord<br/>Multi-service containers]

    %% ML Frameworks (Optional per image variant)
    Notebooks -.->|ML framework| PyTorch[PyTorch<br/>Various versions]
    Notebooks -.->|ML framework| TensorFlow[TensorFlow<br/>Various versions]
    Notebooks -.->|data science| Pandas[pandas ~2.2.0<br/>scikit-learn ~1.4.0]

    %% GPU/Accelerator Support (Optional per hardware)
    Notebooks -.->|GPU| CUDA[CUDA Toolkit<br/>NVIDIA GPU acceleration]
    Notebooks -.->|GPU| ROCm[ROCm<br/>AMD GPU acceleration]
    Notebooks -.->|accelerator| IntelOneAPI[Intel oneAPI<br/>Intel GPU/Habana]

    %% Cloud/External SDKs
    Notebooks -.->|cloud storage| boto3[boto3 ~1.34.50<br/>AWS S3 SDK]
    Notebooks -.->|distributed computing| CodeFlareSDK[codeflare-sdk ~0.19.1<br/>Ray integration]
    Notebooks -.->|pipelines| Elyra[ODH Elyra ~3.16.7<br/>Kubeflow Pipelines]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    NotebookController[notebook-controller] -->|launches pods| Notebooks
    KubeflowNotebooks[kubeflow-notebooks<br/>Notebook CRD] -.->|consumed by| NotebookController
    OAuthProxy[oauth-proxy] -.->|sidecar auth| Notebooks
    ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|lists images| Notebooks
    KFP[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Kubeflow/Tekton] <-.->|Elyra submit| Notebooks
    ModelMesh[Model Mesh] -->|uses runtime images| Notebooks

    %% External Services (Runtime)
    Notebooks -->|install packages| PyPI[PyPI<br/>pypi.org]
    Notebooks -->|install R packages| CRAN[CRAN<br/>cran.rstudio.com]
    Notebooks -->|data access| S3External[S3 Storage<br/>AWS/MinIO]
    Notebooks -->|source code| GitRepos[Git Repositories<br/>GitHub/GitLab]
    Notebooks -->|cluster mgmt| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>OpenShift]

